1. Project Overview

This project implements a DSGVO-compliant video consultation system for Sozialverband VdK.

The system is built on top of Jitsi Meet, but the default Jitsi client is modified to support a strict 1:1 consultation workflow.

The goal is to create a simple, secure video consultation platform that mimics an in-person advisory meeting between:

Advisor (Berater)

Client (Mandant)

Important constraint:

The system must only support two participants.

The project modifies the existing Jitsi Meet React client, rather than creating a new one.

2. Development Principle
DO

Modify the existing Jitsi Meet Web Client.

This includes:

editing React components

removing features

restricting meeting capabilities

customizing UI

integrating token-based access

DO NOT

Build a new WebRTC client

Replace the Jitsi architecture

Implement custom media handling

The Jitsi stack remains unchanged.

